title: Rachel & Becca Discuss Accountability Within Bachelor Nation, Jessenia Joins
description:
Jessenia, who was sent home last night on “The Bachelor,” joins Rachel and Becca to discuss how she thinks race factored into this season. She also opens up about how she thought Matt did in his role as “The Bachelor.”

Plus, Jessenia shares her thoughts on that infamous two-on-one with MJ and explains what led her to tell Matt she was falling in love with him.
